<section id="overview" class="active">
<div class="card">
<h2>What You Will Learn</h2>
<p>In this lesson, you will learn how and why content spreads online using the STEPPS framework. You will apply these ideas to real social media content and your own work.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>STEPPS Framework</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Social Currency:</b> People share things that make them look good</li>
<li><b>Triggers:</b> What reminds people to share</li>
<li><b>Emotion:</b> Content that makes people feel something spreads more</li>
<li><b>Public:</b> Easy-to-see content spreads faster</li>
<li><b>Practical Value:</b> Helpful information gets shared</li>
<li><b>Stories:</b> People share stories, not ads</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>

